C++ program file for hash-table is added

INPUT
It ask for number of words you want to encrypt and then you can enter that number of words to encrypt.

OUTPUT
Each bucket with its contents is shown.

IMPLEMENTATION
Hash table is implemnted using array and linked list, i.e. array of linked-list.
Hashing is done by first taking sum of ASCII value of each charater of the word and then taking modulo of this sum.
Number of buckets can be changed by changing value of 'hashingDivisor' in code
